  95,3,Yaha! M-po tiŇč‚Äô sh…õli din mali suhudoo Ňč…Ē maa (Maka)
  95,4,"Achiika! Ti (Tinim‚Äô Naawuni) namla ninsala, namdi shőĶli din v…õlim paai tariga puuni"
  95,5,"Din nyaaŇča, ka Ti labsi o na, ka o ti ny…õ Ňčun gbargi n-gari sokam (o kurginsim saha)"
  95,6,"Na…£ila ninvu…£u sh…õba ban ti Naawuni y…õlimaŇčli, ka tum tuunsuma, t…Ē! B…õ mali laara din ka Ňčmaabu"
  95,7,"Din nyaaŇča, bo n-leei ch…õ ka a labsi sanyoo (Chiyaama)  íiri"
  95,8,"Di ni b…ĒŇč…Ē, pa Naawuni n-ny…õ Ňäun gari ban kam zaandi fukumsi fukumsi zalibu"
